cast.overview: Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.
cast.title: Ex Machina

details.biography: Dan Pappaspanos is an American actor known for his role in Alex Garland's Ex Machina.
details.name: Dan Pappaspanos
